{"tid":1164140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣8歲男童離奇墮樓 送院搶救","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T01:10:46.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2d373124e2301a2680b3aff0dbccbd42f5a08a","tid":1164140,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"早上8時許，荃灣川龍街135號一名約8、9歲的男童，由高處墮下，跌在大廈1樓簷篷。救護員接報到場將男童送瑪嘉烈醫院搶救，警方初步調查顯示，他由4樓墮下，現正封鎖現場了解事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190521/59623654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59623654&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=ba46ebfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59623654&h=1b7130d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190521/59623654</a>"},{"pid":"663a55fa882217acad38a53ec1f68d16a0e4899c","tid":1164140,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"可能唔想返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196e1fb177961b8c6ca3b37580f5675104fdb478","tid":1164140,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190521/mobile/bkn-20190521082534649-0521_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190521%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190521082534649-0521_00822_001.html&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=74ffb3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190521/mobile/bkn-20190521082534649-0521_00822_001.html</a><br />\n荃灣川龍街135號，今晨(21日)8時02分，有途人發現一名年約8男童由大廈高處墮下，被困在1樓簷篷昏迷，大驚報警。消防接報趕至，將男童救出，交救護車送院搶救，警方正調查其身份及墮樓原因。消息指，男童在4樓家中收衫時懷疑失足墮樓，警員正調查事件。"}]}